 review Apple Positional Audio Codec’s (APAC) capabilities for creating and delivering spatial audio content for the most immersive experiences.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc25-297-learn-about-the-apple-projected-media-profile"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"article","references":{"WWDC25-297-Write-APMP-File":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-297-Write-APMP-File.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"WWDC25-297-Write-APMP-File","type":"image"},"WWDC25.jpg":{"identifier":"WWDC25.jpg","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25.jpg"}],"alt":null,"type":"image"},"WWDC25-Icon.png":{"identifier":"WWDC25-Icon.png","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-Icon.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC25-403-Learn-about-Apple-Immersive-Video-technologies":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc25-403-learn-about-apple-immersive-video-technologies","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-403-Learn-about-Apple-Immersive-Video-technologies","title":"Learn about Apple Immersive Video technologies","role":"sampleCode","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Explore the capabilities of Apple Immersive Video and Apple Spatial Audio Format technologies to create truly immersive experiences. Meet the new ImmersiveMediaSupport framework, which offers functionality to read and write the necessary metadata for enabling Apple Immersive Video. Learn guidelines for encoding and publishing Apple Immersive Video content in standalone files for playback or streaming via HLS.","type":"text"}]},"https://developer.apple.com/documentation/http-live-streaming":{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/http-live-streaming","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"HTTP Live Streaming"}],"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/http-live-streaming","type":"link","title":"HTTP Live Streaming"},"WWDC25-297-APMP-Production-Pipeline":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-297-APMP-Production-Pipeline.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"WWDC25-297-APMP-Production-Pipeline","type":"image"},"https://github.com/Jeehut":{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/Jeehut","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"GitHub","type":"text"}],"title":"GitHub","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/Jeehut","type":"link"},"WWDC25-297-Recomended-Playback-Limits":{"identifier":"WWDC25-297-Recomended-Playback-Limits","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-297-Recomended-Playback-Limits.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"WWDC25-297-Radial-Distortion":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-297-Radial-Distortion.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"WWDC25-297-Radial-Distortion","type":"image"},"Jeehut":{"identifier":"Jeehut","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/Jeehut.jpeg"}],"alt":"Profile image of Cihat Gündüz","type":"image"},"WWDC25-297-Minimal-Ambisonics-Code":{"identifier":"WWDC25-297-Minimal-Ambisonics-Code","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-297-Minimal-Ambisonics-Code.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"https://developer.apple.com/documentation/http-live-streaming/using-apple-s-http-live-streaming-hls-tools":{"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/http-live-streaming\/using-apple-s-http-live-streaming-hls-tools","title":"HLS Tools","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/http-live-streaming\/using-apple-s-http-live-streaming-hls-tools","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"HLS Tools","type":"text"}]},"WWDC25-297-CMTaggedDynamicBuffer":{"identifier":"WWDC25-297-CMTaggedDynamicBuffer","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-297-CMTaggedDynamicBuffer.jpeg"}],"alt":null,"type":"image"},"Jeehut.jpeg":{"identifier":"Jeehut.jpeg","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/Jeehut.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"WWDC25-297-New-Video-Profiles":{"alt":"Table showcasing all supported media profiles, highlighting the new 180, 360, and Wide FOV columns","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-297-New-Video-Profiles.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"WWDC25-297-New-Video-Profiles","type":"image"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png"}],"alt":null,"type":"image"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC25-237-Whats-new-for-the-spatial-web":{"title":"What’s new for the spatial web","type":"topic","role":"sampleCode","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-237-Whats-new-for-the-spatial-web","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc25-237-whats-new-for-the-spatial-web","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Discover the latest spatial features for the web on visionOS 26. We’ll cover how to display inline 3D models with the brand new HTML model element. And we’ll share powerful features, including model lighting, interactions, and animations. Learn how to embed newly supported immersive media on your web site, such as 360-degree video and Apple Immersive Video. And get a sneak peek at adding a custom environment to your web pages."}],"kind":"article"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC25-296-Support-immersive-video-playback-in-visionOS-apps":{"title":"Support immersive video playback in visionOS apps","type":"topic","role":"sampleCode","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC25-296-Support-immersive-video-playback-in-visionOS-apps","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc25-296-support-immersive-video-playback-in-visionos-apps","abstract":[{"text":"Discover how to play immersive videos in visionOS apps. We’ll cover various immersive rendering modes, review the frameworks that support them, and walk thro